**Summary:** Documents Amplitude's AppsFlyer streaming integration for forwarding events and cohorts to AppsFlyer, requiring AppsFlyer S2S Key and App ID authentication, with mandatory AppsFlyer ID mapping and optional device identifier mapping (GAID, IDFA, IDFV, etc.).

**Keywords:**
- AppsFlyer streaming integration
- AppsFlyer S2S Key authentication
- AppsFlyer App ID
- AppsFlyer ID mapping
- Customer User ID mapping
- Device identifier mapping (GAID, IDFA, IDFV, OAID, IMEI)
- Event streaming destination
- Cohort export
- Attribution integration
- AppsFlyer event values
- S2S token management
- Mobile attribution platform